{"tid":1124840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"忠犬用力踮腳…只為見主人最後一面　","createTime":"2019-04-25T09:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T10:39:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":419,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"fc32be657b0a4669e641589960a1c734fe8d8fa8","tid":1124840,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/4047/d4047475.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4047%2Fd4047475.jpg&h=0779c601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Chief和主人的感情如膠似漆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n許多動物與人類之間經常有超越時間和空間的情感連結，尤其是以對人類忠心著稱的狗兒。一隻狗兒在喪禮上用力踮腳、想再看主人一眼的畫面，充滿了對主人的想念和忠心，令所見者無不為之動容，又感到心疼不忍。<br />\n<br />\n感人事件發生在美國北卡羅來納州，76歲的老主人William D. Schiller（Bill）在4月初離世，在追思會上，他生前最親暱的寵物、狗狗Chief也來見他最後一面，在老人孫女拍下的照片中，Chief用力再用力的踮著腳尖，只為了離心愛的主人更近一點，因為牠知道，這就是最後一次見面了。<br />\n<br />\nBill的伴侶Anne目擊這一幕，她說「Chief不斷想伸長脖子，希望舔舔Bill的耳朵，但他卻沒有任何反應，讓Chief很傷心、顯得悶悶不樂。」Anne表示，她在2014年時帶Chief回家，原本是要幫流浪的Chief找一個新家，沒想到牠和Bill一拍即合，成為他晚年生活最重要的心靈支柱。<br />\n<br />\n很顯然Chief也知道主人對牠的愛，而牠在主人喪禮上的追悼畫面，也感動無數網友，為Chief的忠心感到動容，「希望牠趕快走出傷痛，之後能幫助更多人。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/4047/d4047473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4047%2Fd4047473.jpg&h=c116cf86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Chief在主人喪禮上這幕被拍了下來，讓許多人都掉了眼淚。（圖／翻攝自IG／nina__photography_06）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/4047/d4047477.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4047%2Fd4047477.jpg&h=455cc17c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/4047/d4047476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4047%2Fd4047476.jpg&h=89f6c1e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.ettoday.net/images/4047/d4047472.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4047%2Fd4047472.jpg&h=0dbccf18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1429614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpets.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1429614&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SfaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=b99653f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pets.ettoday.net/news/1429614</a>"},{"pid":"caea93d8ec9c6d25b40bc506c103e82dd5b03397","tid":1124840,"uid":50658,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931d819a2af39354367a44f35c748426dcf117a4","tid":1124840,"uid":8647,"like":54,"dislike":150,"score":-96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"看圖作文"},{"pid":"2a28c15fe60bf1b37cab0de9e3cfe49f4fbc493c","tid":1124840,"uid":114275,"like":17,"dislike":56,"score":-39,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"然後有連登仔會話狗係無感情嘅"},{"pid":"1a521d14f1ba1786deabfec60ec21993f921642e","tid":1124840,"uid":46849,"like":17,"dislike":71,"score":-54,"quote":{"pid":"2a28c15fe60bf1b37cab0de9e3cfe49f4fbc493c","tid":1124840,"uid":114275,"like":17,"dislike":56,"score":-39,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"然後有連登仔會話狗係無感情嘅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"因為係食物黎"},{"pid":"6870845f4dd79848bf5ac19aad6fb7336453eb30","tid":1124840,"uid":50740,"like":4,"dislike":27,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"1a521d14f1ba1786deabfec60ec21993f921642e","tid":1124840,"uid":46849,"like":17,"dislike":71,"score":-54,"quote":{"pid":"2a28c15fe60bf1b37cab0de9e3cfe49f4fbc493c","tid":1124840,"uid":114275,"like":17,"dislike":56,"score":-39,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"然後有連登仔會話狗係無感情嘅"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"因為係食物黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T10:06:59.000Z","msg":"一陣有人貼狗肉圖"},{"pid":"76a83c9c4ec66b14e8b8966c6c1581c3814fca4a","tid":1124840,"uid":64601,"like":57,"dislike":7,"sc